Hello,


I present to you Spider Deploy, developed by me with SAPIEN POWERSHELL STUDIO

Allows you to add and remove computers to SCCM collections. (System Center Configuration Manager).



required : 

- SCCM must be installed in your computer.

- You must change setting in ps1

#----------------------------------------------# VARIABLES#----------------------------------------------

 $script:site = "YourCODESITE"

 $script:Server = "YourServerSCCM"
